node.text: Didnt know  @tonggardensg has potato chips and sticks! Wow’

Thank you @tonggardensg for the goodies! My little prince love the can of coconut flavour coated peanuts 😘 the most while mummy here love all the chips! My mum immediately took the chestnuts 😅 My hubby took the dried guava and my eldest son, the seaweed. There’s really something for everyone in the family! 🙆🏻‍♀️
